MSE operational in management?: There is no shortage of management plans evaluated for NSAS herring, and the latest evaluation is given in column H. However, this is a jointly-managed stock (EU and Norway, soon to become EU, UK and Norway) and the different parties have not agreed a management plan, so ICES advises according to their next best option, i.e. their MSY approach.
